You seem like you are having problem socializing and you stay on computer most of a time.I used to have similiar moments (I'm 18 now).I was playing games most of a time with some friends to relax and stop thinking about problems(at least my case).Please stop playing games,they will destroy you or at least play 1-2 hours a day.Start training basketball if you are short or go to gym.Video games decrease your testosteron and will give you tired nerd look forever.Look up if you are having"nerd neck" or "lordosis".If you have fix asap or you will ruin yourself.You don't want typical gamer look.You are still growing and having lots of time to fix yourself.Look up mewing(method of changing face to better),do sports or go to gym,draw,listen to music more or go to concerts,watch movies rather than playing games and more things.I wish i never played video games i could change lots of things in my life instead take that and good luck.
